\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\f1 REAPER Audio Tag} is a REAPER action for local clip-level audio tagging.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 ReaPack installs the Lua UI and a platform backend. On first run, click {\f1 Download Model} to fetch the ONNX Cnn14 model into REAPER's data folder.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 No user-managed Python, venv, or manual model file selection is required.\par}
}
